org.jfree.data

Interface XYZDataset

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Dataset, SeriesDataset, XYDataset
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ContourDataset, IntervalXYZDataset
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractXYZDataset, DefaultContourDataset, MatrixSeriesCollection, NonGridContourDataset, SampleXYZDataset

    public interface XYZDataset
extends XYDataset
    The interface through which JFreeChart obtains data in the form of (x, y, z) items - used for XY and XYZ plots.
